    <statement><p>Multiply the polynomials.</p>
<p><m>\left({r+9}\right)\left({r+1}\right)=</m><fillin characters="32" name="AnSwEr0001"/></p>
</statement>
    <answer>
      <p>
        <m>r^{2}+10r+9</m>
      </p>
    </answer>
    <solution><p>We use the FOIL technique- <alert>F</alert>irst <alert>O</alert>utside <alert>I</alert>nside <alert>L</alert>ast</p>
<p><m>\begin{aligned}
              \left({r+9}\right)({r+1})\amp ={r^{2}+r+9r+9}\\
                                \amp ={r^{2}+10r+9}
      \end{aligned}</m></p>
</solution>
